[@Lisias](https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/187168-lisias/) & [@pellinor](https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/85299-pellinor/) I have a defaultscale.cfg that adds 1.875 along with .938, and 3.125 scales to it. The eleviates the need to add custom scalefactors for 1.875m parts like all the MH parts. I also added a few other increments to surface, free and free\_square that I use frequently: .25, .75 and 1.5

You're welcome to use it if you'd like.

Spoiler

